# Production SSH (paperclip-vm)

Production runs on **paperclip-vm** (`140.245.14.17`) as Docker (`twcto_docker`), not the retired EC2 instance.

| Setting | Value |
|--------|--------|
| **Host** | `140.245.14.17` |
| **SSH config alias** | `paperclip` (in `~/.ssh/config`) |
| **User** | `ubuntu` |
| **Private key** | `~/.ssh/paperclip_key` |
| **App compose** | `/home/ubuntu/twcto` ([bipulsin/twcto_docker](https://github.com/bipulsin/twcto_docker)) |
| **Public URLs** | `https://www.tradewithcto.com`, `https://twcto.tradentical.com` |

## Commands

```bash
# Interactive shell
ssh paperclip
# or
./scripts/paperclip-ssh.sh

# One-off remote command
./scripts/paperclip-ssh.sh 'cd /home/ubuntu/twcto && docker compose ps'
```

## Deploy (after pushing TradeManthan to GitHub)

```bash
REBUILD=1 ./scripts/trigger-paperclip-deploy.sh
# or commit + push + deploy:
./scripts/release-push-and-deploy.sh -m "your message"
```

`REBUILD=1` rebuilds `app` + `nginx` images cloning latest `bipulsin/trademanthan` `main`.  
Docker packaging / compose changes go to **bipulsin/twcto_docker** (not TradeManthan).

## Logs

```bash
./scripts/paperclip-ssh.sh 'cd /home/ubuntu/twcto && docker compose logs -f --tail=50 app'
```

## Security

- Never commit SSH private keys or `.env` secrets.
- `TradeM.pem` was for the old EC2 — do not use for paperclip-vm.
